AsyncCallback<T>
public abstract class PanelCallback<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements AsyncCallback<T>

A base class for callbacks that automatically report errors by clearing a target Panel and adding a Label to it. The label will be styled as errorLabel, a basic style for which is defined in the CSS file accompanying this library.
